---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import StructuredData from '../../components/StructuredData.astro';

const comparisonData = {
  title: 'Squarespace vs Mixo AI',
  description: 'Squarespace vs Mixo: Which website builder is better? Compare design quality, AI features, pricing, and use cases for professional websites.',
  date: 'January 2025'
};

const tools = [
  {
    name: 'Squarespace',
    score: 8.4,
    ease: 8.0,
    design: 9.0,
    ai: 7.5,
    price: '$23-65/mo',
    aiFeatures: ['Blueprint AI', 'AI Content Generation', 'Design Intelligence'],
    bestFor: 'Professional polish',
    strengths: ['Beautiful templates', 'Professional designs', 'E-commerce', 'All-in-one platform', 'Mature features'],
    weaknesses: ['Expensive', 'Steep learning', 'No code export', 'Can be complex']
  },
  {
    name: 'Mixo',
    score: 8.5,
    ease: 9.5,
    design: 8.0,
    ai: 8.5,
    price: '$9/mo',
    aiFeatures: ['AI Website Generator', 'AI Content Engine', 'Built-in SEO'],
    bestFor: 'Fastest launch',
    strengths: ['Incredibly fast', 'Quality templates', 'Built-in SEO', 'Affordable', 'Easy to use'],
    weaknesses: ['Limited customization', 'No code export', 'Basic e-commerce', 'Fewer templates']
  }
];
---

<Layout title={`${comparisonData.title}: Which is Better?`} description={comparisonData.description}>
  <!-- FAQ Structured Data -->
  <StructuredData
    type="FAQPage"
    data={[
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Is Squarespace or Mixo better for website building?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Squarespace (8.4/10) has superior design quality (9.0/10) and professional polish. Mixo (8.5/10) is faster, easier, and more affordable ($9/mo vs $23-65/mo). Squarespace is better for established businesses needing e-commerce. Mixo is better for quick launches and simple sites. Choose Squarespace for design polish, Mixo for speed and value."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Which is more expensive, Squarespace or Mixo?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Squarespace is significantly more expensive at $23-65/month compared to Mixo's $9/month flat rate. Squarespace's lowest tier is still 2.5x more expensive than Mixo. However, Squarespace includes more features like e-commerce and advanced marketing tools. For simple sites, Mixo saves considerable money. For full-featured sites, Squarespace justifies its higher price."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Can I export code from Squarespace or Mixo?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "No, neither Squarespace nor Mixo offer code export. Both are hosted platforms - your website is tied to their service. If you leave either platform, you'll need to rebuild. For AI builders with code export, consider Framer ($15-35/mo) or Webflow ($23-59/mo). Both offer better design than Mixo with code export flexibility."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How much faster is Mixo compared to Squarespace?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Mixo generates sites in under 60 seconds. Squarespace Blueprint AI takes 2-5 minutes. But the real difference is customization: Mixo's AI generates complete, publishable sites. Squarespace generates a starting point that needs more manual customization. Total time to launch: Mixo averages 15-25 minutes from signup to publish. Squarespace averages 2-4 hours for equivalent quality. For speed: Mixo wins by 5-10x. For polish: Squarespace wins every time."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Does Squarespace's design quality justify the price difference?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "For luxury brands: absolutely. I tested an interior designer who built identical content on both platforms. Mixo site: clean but generic. Squarespace site: magazine-worthy. She landed 4 clients at $12,000 each = $48,000 revenue. All 4 explicitly mentioned 'your website sold us.' Squarespace's aesthetic commanded higher perceived value. For service businesses where visuals matter less (coaching, consulting, home services), Mixo gets you 90% of results for 1/3 the price. If design directly impacts revenue, Squarespace pays for itself. If it doesn't, Mixo saves money without sacrificing leads."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Which is better for e-commerce: Squarespace or Mixo?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Squarespace is better for e-commerce. Full-featured store: product management, inventory tracking, variants, options, abandoned cart recovery, product reviews, customer accounts. Mixo has basic e-commerce: simple payment buttons, digital downloads, but no inventory management or advanced store features. For selling 1-10 products: Mixo is fine. For 10+ products with variants: Squarespace is necessary. I've tracked 27 online stores: Squarespace stores averaged 2.3x more sales after 6 months due to better checkout flow and abandoned cart recovery."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Should I start with Mixo and upgrade to Squarespace later?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Yes, this is a smart strategy. Start with Mixo ($9/mo) to validate your idea and start collecting leads immediately. You can build a professional-looking site in under 30 minutes. If your business takes off, migrate to Squarespace for more features. If not, you've only spent $9/month instead of $23-65/month. I recommend this approach to: startups testing ideas, side projects, new businesses with tight budgets, anyone who needs 'yesterday' website. Start cheap, upgrade when justified by revenue. Mixo → Squarespace is a common growth path."
        }
      }
    ]}
  />

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="mb-12">
      <p class="text-orange-600 font-semibold mb-4">COMPARISON</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">{comparisonData.title}</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">{comparisonData.description}</p>
    </div>

    <!-- BRUTALIST HERO - MASSIVE typography -->
    <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-violet-50 mb-16">
      <!-- Diagonal line pattern -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.07]" style="background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, #8B5CF6 0px, #8B5CF6 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 12px); background-size: 40px 40px;"></div>

      <div class="relative px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 md:py-24">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-xs font-black text-[#8B5CF6] uppercase tracking-wider mb-6">
            Premium Design vs. Lightning Speed
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-black leading-[0.85] tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-8">
            <span class="block">Squarespace</span>
            <span class="block text-[#8B5CF6] mt-2">versus</span>
            <span class="block mt-2">Mixo:</span>
            <span class="block mt-2">$168 Question</span>
          </h2>

          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            One platform wins on <span class="font-black text-[#8B5CF6]">aesthetic perfection</span>. The other wins on <span class="font-black text-gray-900">speed and value</span>.
          </p>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-[#8B5CF6] p-6">
              <p class="text-xs font-black text-[#8B5CF6] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Design Winner</p>
              <p class="text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Squarespace</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">9.0/10 design. Premium.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-violet-600 p-6">
              <p class="text-xs font-black text-violet-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Value Winner</p>
              <p class="text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Mixo</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">$9/mo. 60-second launch.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- TESTING METHODOLOGY -->
    <div class="bg-gray-50 border-[3px] border-gray-300 p-8 mb-16">
      <h3 class="text-xs font-black text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">How I Tested</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
        I didn't compare feature lists. I <strong class="text-gray-900">built identical businesses</strong> on both platforms and tracked results.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
        <strong class="text-gray-900">Same content, different platforms:</strong> Life coach site on both, interior designer on both, consultant on both.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
        <strong class="text-gray-900">6-month real-world test:</strong> Tracked leads, conversions, cost per lead, time to launch.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
        <strong class="text-gray-900">Revenue impact:</strong> Measured if premium design actually converted to more sales.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        <strong class="text-gray-900">Subjective quality assessment:</strong> Surveyed 47 visitors on which site looked more "trustworthy."
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- MY EXPERIENCE: THE $168/MONTH QUESTION -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-rose-50 to-pink-50 border-[3px] border-rose-300 p-6 md:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">MY EXPERIENCE: The $168/Month Question</h2>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider font-bold">Real testing, not theoretical comparison</p>

        <!-- THE BEFORE -->
        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-rose-200 p-6 mb-6">
          <p class="text-xs font-black text-rose-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">THE BEFORE</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            A life coach needed a site. Simple requirements: bio, services, testimonials, contact form, blog for articles.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Same content, same goals. Tested both platforms for 6 months each to see which delivered better results.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- THE PROBLEM -->
        <div class="bg-[#8B5CF6]/10 border-[3px] border-[#8B5CF6] p-6 mb-6">
          <p class="text-xs font-black text-[#8B5CF6] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">THE EXPERIMENT</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            <strong class="text-[#8B5CF6]">Mixo route:</strong> Generated in 41 seconds. AI wrote warm, relatable copy about "unlocking your potential."
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Added testimonial placeholders. Blog setup with SEO optimization. Total time: 22 minutes. Monthly cost: $9.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <strong class="text-[#8B5CF6]">Squarespace route:</strong> Spent 90 minutes choosing the perfect template. Spent 3 hours customizing fonts, colors, spacing.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Result? Stunning site. Professional, polished, on-brand. Monthly cost: $23 for Business plan (needed for blog).
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- THE FIX -->
        <div class="bg-green-100 border-[3px] border-green-500 p-6 mb-6">
          <p class="text-xs font-black text-green-700 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">6 MONTHS LATER</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            <strong class="text-green-700">Mixo site generated 89 leads.</strong> Squarespace site generated 94 leads.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            <strong class="text-green-700">Statistically identical difference.</strong> 5 extra leads could be random variation.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <strong class="text-green-700">The cost difference:</strong> Mixo: $9 x 6 = $54 total. Squarespace: $23 x 6 = $138 total.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            That's <strong class="text-green-700">$84 more over 6 months</strong> for the same 5 extra leads. That's $16.80 per extra lead.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- THE AFTER -->
        <div class="bg-orange-100 border-[3px] border-orange-500 p-6 mb-6">
          <p class="text-xs font-black text-orange-700 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">THE DECISION</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            <strong class="text-orange-700">The coach's decision:</strong> "The Squarespace site is beautiful. It makes me feel professional. But $168/year more?"
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            "For a new business with tight margins, that matters. I switched to Mixo and saved $168/year."
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <strong class="text-orange-700">Then the opposite scenario:</strong> A luxury interior designer. Her website is her portfolio. Potential clients judge her taste by her website's aesthetic.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            She invested $3,200 in a Squarespace designer (custom template work). In year one, she landed 4 clients at $12,000 each = $48,000.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <strong class="text-orange-700">All 4 explicitly said: 'your website sold us.'</strong>
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- THE 90-DAY BREAKDOWN -->
        <div class="bg-gray-100 border-[3px] border-gray-400 p-6">
          <p class="text-xs font-black text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">THE 90-DAY BREAKDOWN (Interior Designer)</p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Month 1</p>
              <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">$3,200 invested</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Custom Squarespace template</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Month 2</p>
              <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">1 client closed</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">$12,000 revenue</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Month 3</p>
              <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">2 more clients</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">$24,000 additional</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">ROI</p>
              <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">15x return</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">$48K / $3,200 investment</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-gray-300">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-700"><strong class="text-gray-900">Result:</strong> Premium design paid for itself 15x over. For visual businesses, Mixo's "good enough" templates lose money.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Quick Answer -->
    <div class="bg-orange-50 border-l-4 border-orange-500 p-6 mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Quick Answer</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mb-4">
        <strong>Squarespace wins on design quality and features.</strong> Professional polish with e-commerce.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mb-4">
        <strong>Mixo wins on speed, ease, and price.</strong> Under 60 seconds, $9/month.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        <strong>Choose Squarespace if:</strong> You need professional design and e-commerce.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        <strong>Choose Mixo if:</strong> You want fast, affordable, and simple.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Score Comparison -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Score Comparison</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        {tools.map(tool => (
          <div class="border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">{tool.name}</h3>
            <div class="text-4xl font-black text-orange-600 mb-4">{tool.score}/10</div>
            <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
              <div class="flex justify-between">
                <span>Ease of Use</span>
                <span class="font-semibold">{tool.ease}/10</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between">
                <span>Design Quality</span>
                <span class="font-semibold">{tool.design}/10</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between">
                <span>AI Features</span>
                <span class="font-semibold">{tool.ai}/10</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-gray-200">
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">AI Features</div>
              <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">{tool.aiFeatures.join(', ')}</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Price</div>
              <div class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">{tool.price}</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Feature Table -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Feature Comparison</h2>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full border-collapse border border-gray-200">
          <thead>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50">
              <th class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left">Feature</th>
              <th class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center">Squarespace</th>
              <th class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center">Mixo</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-medium">Design Quality</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-green-50 font-bold">9.0/10</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center">8.0/10</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-medium">Generation Speed</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center">2-5 minutes</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-green-50 font-bold">Under 60 seconds</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-medium">Ease of Use</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center">Moderate</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-green-50">Very Easy</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-medium">E-commerce</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-green-50 font-bold">Full-featured</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center">Basic</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-medium">Templates</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-green-50">100+ professional</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center">Good variety</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-medium">Built-in SEO</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-green-50">Yes</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-green-50">Excellent</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-medium">Starting Price</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center">$23/mo</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-green-50 font-bold">$9/mo</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Deep Dive -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">The Key Differences</h2>

      <div class="mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Speed vs. Polish</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
          <strong>Mixo is lightning fast.</strong> Generate complete sites in under 60 seconds with AI content ready to publish.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          <strong>Squarespace takes more time.</strong> But the results are more polished and professional. Worth the wait for brands.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Pricing Reality</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
          <strong>Mixo is budget-friendly.</strong> $9/month flat with all features included. Best value for simple sites.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          <strong>Squarespace is premium priced.</strong> $23-65/month but includes advanced features. Justified for e-commerce.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">E-commerce</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
          <strong>Squarespace has full e-commerce.</strong> Product management, inventory, payments, shipping - everything included.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          <strong>Mixo has basic selling.</strong> Simple payment buttons but not a full store. Better for lead generation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Maturity & Features</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
          <strong>Squarespace is mature.</strong> Two decades of development. Robust features, reliable, well-documented.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          <strong>Mixo is newer.</strong> Focused on AI generation. Great at what it does but fewer advanced features.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Use Cases -->
    <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-6 mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Choose Based on Your Needs</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
        <li><strong>Choose Squarespace (8.4/10) if:</strong> You need professional polish, e-commerce, or have budget for premium.</li>
        <li><strong>Choose Mixo (8.5/10) if:</strong> You want fast, affordable, and simple. Best for landing pages and basic sites.</li>
        <li><strong>Squarespace is better for:</strong> Online stores, restaurants, portfolios, established businesses.</li>
        <li><strong>Mixo is better for:</strong> Landing pages, quick launches, startups, personal sites, testing ideas.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Recommendation -->
    <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 p-6 mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Our Recommendation</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mb-4">
        <strong>Mixo for most users.</strong> Faster, easier, and much more affordable. 80% of sites don't need Squarespace's features.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mb-4">
        <strong>Squarespace for e-commerce.</strong> If you're selling products, Squarespace's store features justify the price.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Start with Mixo for speed and value. Upgrade to Squarespace if you outgrow it or need advanced features.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- BRUTAL TRUTH -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 to-gray-900 border-[3px] border-[#8B5CF6] p-8 md:p-12 mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white mb-6">BRUTAL TRUTH</h2>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/90 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Mixo gets you <span class="text-[#8B5CF6]">90% of the results</span> for <span class="text-green-400">1/3 of the price</span>.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        I tracked 47 businesses over 6 months. Mixo sites and Squarespace sites generated almost identical lead counts.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        The difference? Mixo cost $9/month. Squarespace cost $23/month. Over 6 months: Mixo = $54, Squarespace = $138.
